<SLUG> BC-BRAVES-METS-NLCS-1STWRITETHRU </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    Braves top Mets, win NLCS 10-9 in 11-inning nail-biter
 &HT;    (EDS: Corrects to Cox News Service, Atlanta Journal-Constitution
tagline.)
 &HT;    By Carroll Rogers
 &HT;    c. 1999 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
