<HEADLINE>
NISSAN WIELDS AX ON JOBS, PLANTS, SPENDING  
 
</HEADLINE>
   (This 475-word ``separate buy'' article is from the Asahi News
Service.)  
  
 (EDITORS: Get your news from Japan and the Pacific Rim straight
from the source _ the Asahi News Service. Its Monday through Friday
