<HEADLINE>
NYERERE: AFRICAN LEADER MADE A DIFFERENCE FOR THE BETTER  
 
</HEADLINE>
  
 (ATTN: Commentary Editors)   (This 400-word ``separate buy'' commentary is from THE INDEPENDENT
newspaper in London.)  
  
 (EDITORS: We regret that this material is NOT available to clients
in Canada EXCEPT to The Hamilton (Ontario) Spectator.)  
  
