<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    ATTN: Re-sending for those papers that have not used it
previously.
 &HT;    LETTER FROM HONDURAS: AFTER DISASTER, REBUILDING HOMES IS NOT
ENOUGH
 &HT;    With Photos, including mug of Williams.
