(Pantheon). Reviewed by Christopher Lehmann-Haupt.
</P>
<P>
   BOOK-TALK (Undated) _ The weekly books column. By Martin Arnold.
</P>
<P>
   TV-TOBACCO-REVIEW (Undated) _ On TLC, ``Tobacco Wars,'' with
Walter Cronkite, in two parts, with part 2 on Friday. Reviewed by
Walter Goodman.
</P>
