r v BC-PAGEEXPRESS-BUDGET-UP     10-20 0158
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-PAGEEXPRESS-BUDGET-UPDATE-NYTSF </SLUG>
 
<TEXT>
<P>
   Here is the budget for this week's NASCAR page, which will be
available to PageExpress today before 5 p.m.
</P>
<P>
   &UR; NASCAR &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   BENSON PROFILE: Johnny Benson says he is not panicking yet, even
though he still doesn't have a ride for next season and most of the
prime jobs already have been filled. Benson is parting ways with
Roush Racing after the Atlanta race because of back-to-back
disappointing years. What went wrong? What is he going to do about
next season?
</P>
