   ATMS _ ATMs soon could become vending machines that dispense
phone cards, stamps, movie tickets and other items. First Union is
selling phone time through all of its ATMs in Florida, and it's
selling stamps at some machines. NationsBank says it isn't
following suit because customers don't want to wait in line behind
an ATM customer on a shopping trip. (Ostrowski, Palm Beach Post).
10.
</P>
