have magnetic resonance imaging tests either Thursday or Friday:
Robin Ventura (left knee), Darryl Hamilton (left knee), Edgardo
Alfonzo (right knee), Al Leiter (left knee), John Franco (right
knee) and Benny Agbayani (left elbow). Billy Taylor will have left
knee surgery and Armando Benitez's left ankle will also be looked
at. ... Mike Piazza was taken out of Game 6 because, Bobby
Valentine said, his right shoulder was causing him pain and it was
affecting his ability to throw.
</P>
