</P>
<P>
   WTO-BROWNER (Seattle) _ A boisterous crowd of eco-demonstators
challenged the United States' head environmental regulator
yesterday when she came to Seattle with a seemingly conciliatory
message: The World Trade Organization, properly tweaked, could help
preserve the earth.
</P>
