<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-10-20 23:21 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A3537 &Cx1f; taf-z
u k BC-EDIT-DOLENYT &LR;      10-20 0460
